### Offline batch sync (guide only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{guideToken}}

{
  "attempts": [
    {
      "clientId": "offline-attempt-001",
      "quizId": "{{quizId}}",
      "attemptNumber": 1,
      "submittedAt": "2026-04-15T08:30:00.000Z",
      "responses": [
        {
          "questionId": "REPLACE_WITH_QUESTION_ID",
          "selectedOptionId": "REPLACE_WITH_OPTION_ID"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### Sync with empty attempts array (expect 200 with empty results)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/sync
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{guideToken}}

{
  "attempts": []
}
